      <sect1 id="VideoHardwareSpecifications"> 
      <title>Video Hardware Specifications</title>
        <sect2 id="GraphicCard">
        <title>Graphic Card </title>
        <para>The graphic card will manage your video output. The choice of your graphic card will depend on how you want to use Scenic. For now, we only support nvidia video card. Some ATI cards have problems with Xvideo extension. YMMV.
        Before choosing your graphic card. Determine the following needs:
